Задача 6:

![image](https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4bc0c51f-e742-4284-825c-f380397dae63)

Листинг:
```C++
#include <fstream>
using namespace std;
int main() {
    ifstream in("banner.c");
    string line;
    getline(in, line);
    if (line[0] == '/') {
        if (line[1] == '/' || line[1] == '*')
            printf("Success\n");
        else {
            printf("Not success\n");
        }
    }
    else {
        printf("Not success\n");
    }
}
```
